The '''2014 USA Sevens Collegiate Rugby Championship''' was a [[rugby sevens]] tournament. The tournament was held on May 30 — June 1 at [[PPL Park]] in [[Chester, Pennsylvania]].<ref>[http://www.philadelphiaunion.com/ppl-park/collegiaterugbychampionship ""Collegiate Rugby Championship"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006085154/http://www.philadelphiaunion.com/ppl-park/collegiaterugbychampionship |date=2014-10-06 }}, Philadelphia Union. Retrieved October 1, 2014.</ref> It was the fifth annual [[Collegiate Rugby Championship]], and the fourth consecutive year that the tournament is held at PPL Park. [[California Golden Bears rugby|California]] defeated [[Kutztown Golden Bears|Kutztown]] 24-21 in the final to secure the CRC Championship for the second year in a row.<ref>{{cite web|title=2014 Fixtures And Results|url=http://www.usasevenscrc.com/2014-fixtures-and-results/|website=Collegiate Rugby Championship|publisher=United World Sports, LLC}}</ref><ref>[http://olympictalk.nbcsports.com/2015/05/28/collegiate-rugby-championship-crc-preview-sevens/ "Cal favored to make history at Collegiate Rugby Championship"], NBC OlympicTalk, Nick Zaccardi, May 28, 2015.</ref>

